title: I just setup my Google work profile on my Google Pixel 5. I can't sign into my Google work account
content: I tried resetting my network connection, deleted profile, re-installed, tried to sync manually, so far keep getting the error on my Google Account Screen: Finishing signing in to continue, Something went wrong and you need to sign in again. When I attempt to do so, the screen flashes and takes me back to the same error
